   - If you cannot find the exact hash in the code, omit the URL from expected results rather than guessing
8. **NEVER include transient UI states in expected results:**
   - Loading spinners, "Generating...", "Saving..." text, skeleton loaders — these disappear within seconds
   - Toast notifications ("Thought captured!", "Drafts generated!", "Saved!") — gone before verification runs
   - Success/error flashes, progress indicators, any state that auto-dismisses
